### Problem Description

`noop_update_total` is not being updated when using the `_bulk`, but it is being updated when using the `_update`.

### Steps to Reproduce

Bulk
```
DELETE noop_update_demo
// index
POST noop_update_demo/_bulk
{"create":{"_id":"1"}}
{"foo":"bar"}
{"create":{"_id":"2"}}
{"foo":"bar"}

// noop update
POST noop_update_demo/_bulk
{"update":{"_id":"1"}}
{"doc":{"foo": "bar"}}
{"update":{"_id":"2"}}
{"doc":{"foo": "bar"}}

// index_total = 2, noop_update_total = 0 (should be 2)
GET _stats?filter_path=indices.noop_update_demo.total.indexing
```
Return:
```json
{
  "indices": {
    "noop_update_demo": {
      "total": {
        "indexing": {
